        Hi, I'm <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-cyan-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-lg">Aditya Kumar</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white font-semibold mb-4 animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-200">
      Senior Software Engineer at <span class="text-cyan-400">Microsoft</span>
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-400 drop-shadow-md">
      Building scalable cloud solutions on GitHub Codespaces. Passionate about crafting robust, dependable software that empowers developers globally.
    </p>
    
